@VDalibard your symptoms sound similar to mine:

-When you exit python after having loaded tensorflow, it segfaults, but I think everything before works fine.

I got my build to work now, by building a -std=c++11 version of protobuf.  See #2646.  I think this may also apply to everyone else in this issue, but I don't know for sure.

